songs.title: After Pain
songs.lyrics:
Actually, I feel very good
In fact, like a little food

I realized (fix)
You're better without me
This time I will let you be

I'll add volume to the music
I'll listen HeavyMetal all night
And I'll get into fights

I will sing like crazy
I will sing to all lungs

Find someone better than me
But remember that my promise is still valid

I'll talk like crazy
I will speak to all lungs (I will scream)

I'll add volume to the music
I'll listen HeavyMetal all night
And I'll get into fights

I will sing like crazy
I will sing to all lungs
